fullScanPercent.description:
Fraction of the (post-exclusion) unstructured data volume that is fully scanned rather than
sampled (0-1). Only the fully-scanned share counts toward the Download Worker requirement;
values below 1.0 reduce the calculated workload accordingly.

dataReductionPct.description:
Percentage by which the workload's data is reduced through compression — "compress BY", not
"compress TO" (e.g. 20 means the data ends up at roughly 80% of its original size). 0–100;
unstructured data is often pre-compressed, so values above ~25–30% are uncommon.
